					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/toadking07" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1632267); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1632267&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610227335" alt="toadking07" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1632267)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/toadking07" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1632267); return false;" >toadking07</a></span> <span class="odate time_1390338871 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">21 Jan 2014 21:14</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1942283">
									

<p>Yay! Image was just being updated at the exact moment you clicked on the link. Still not sure about the text before hand, but felt the image shouldn't be just floating there alone.</p>
<p>This image/tale is a spin off from my earlier chalk symbols which you can find either posted on the <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-662082">forums here</a> or on <a href="http://toadking07.deviantart.com/art/SCP-Chalk-Symbols-Batch-1-378182689">dA here</a> <sub>(commenting and favoriting encouraged there).</sub></p>
<p>Special thanks to Roget for continuing to poke me about this until it was completed. More thanks go out to PeppersGhost for some last minute artistic feedback, though whether or not I was able to pull it off properly will be seen. Thanks to Aelanna for fixing the markup as well. :P</p>
<p>Also, the Serpent's Hand logo is from <a href="http://www.deviantart.com/art/The-Serpent-s-Hand-03-378358546">SunnyParallax's design</a>.</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
