<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>You can see more of my work online on <a href="https://instagram.com/scpfamradio">Instagram</a> or on <a href="https://youtube.com/toadkingstudios1/">youtube</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>EDIT 4/2/19: SCP Illustrated has made a video covering the MTF symbols where this concept started! Check it out <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VxQvjtcWLu4">on Youtube here</a>!</p>
